---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import founderImg from '../assets/images/imgi_5_tt-206.jpg';
import productsImg from '../assets/images/imgi_3_Body_care.png';
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2]" id="about">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 py-24 lg:py-36">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center mb-24 lg:mb-28">
      <div
        x-data
        x-intersect.once="$el.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-y-0')"
        class="opacity-0 translate-y-6 transition-all duration-700 lg:col-span-5 lg:pb-12"
      >
        <p class="text-[#B8950A] text-sm tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-medium mb-5">Brand Mission</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-[clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3.5rem)] leading-[1.02] text-charcoal-800 mb-7">
          We believe better skin care should feel
          <em class="italic text-[#B8950A]"> calm, inclusive, and clear.</em>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-charcoal-500 leading-relaxed mb-5 text-base">
          CFC Skincare is the bridge between clinical efficacy and clean beauty: a medical-grade, plant-based system created by a nurse practitioner and shaped for women who are done guessing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal-500 leading-relaxed mb-10 text-base">
          Every formula is designed to be gentle enough for daily use, structured enough to guide real routines, and grounded in the kind of oversight that usually never reaches direct-to-consumer skincare.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          {[
            ['Confidence in every bottle', 'Products made to feel wearable and effective.'],
            ['Timeless formulas', 'Routine staples instead of trend chasing.'],
            ['For every stage', 'Designed for changing skin needs over time.'],
            ['Pure and ethical', 'Plant-based formulas with measured discipline.'],
          ].map(([title, desc]) => (
            <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-[#E8E0D5] rounded-[1.5rem]">
              <p class="text-charcoal-800 text-sm font-semibold mb-1 tracking-wide">{title}</p>
              <p class="text-charcoal-400 text-sm leading-snug">{desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        x-data
        x-intersect.once="$el.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-x-0')"
        class="opacity-0 translate-x-6 transition-all duration-700 delay-150 lg:col-span-7 relative"
      >
        <Image
          src={founderImg}
          alt="CFC Skincare founder imagery"
          class="w-full rounded-[2.5rem] object-cover object-top"
          style="max-height: 620px;"
          widths={[600, 900, 1200]}
          sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 58vw"
        />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-4 lg:-left-10 max-w-xs bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]">
          <div class="flex gap-1 text-[#C9A84C] mb-3 text-sm">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="font-serif text-charcoal-700 text-base leading-relaxed italic">
            "I finally found a routine that feels polished, not punishing."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-400 text-sm mt-3 tracking-wide">— CFC Customer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      x-data
      x-intersect.once="$el.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-y-0')"
      class="opacity-0 translate-y-6 transition-all duration-700 grid lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center"
    >
      <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden border border-[#e8dcc9]">
        <Image
          src={productsImg}
          alt="CFC Skincare product collection"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          style="max-height: 500px;"
          widths={[500, 800]}
          sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-[#B8950A] text-sm tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-medium mb-5">Why It Feels Different</p>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-[clamp(1.8rem,2.8vw,2.75rem)] leading-tight text-charcoal-800 mb-6">
          Clinical enough to trust.
          <br />
          Soft enough to live with.
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          {[
            'Compared with luxury skincare, CFC stays focused on function instead of ceremony alone.',
            'Compared with harsher clinical brands, the formulas keep comfort and consistency in the conversation.',
            'Compared with trend-led clean beauty, the system is organized like a real care plan, not a mood board.',
          ].map(line => (
            <p class="flex gap-3 text-charcoal-500 text-base leading-relaxed">
              <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 shrink-0">—</span>
              {line}
            </p>
          ))}
        </div>
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-medium text-[#B8950A] group hover:gap-5 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Request a consultation
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-[#C9A84C] group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
